{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-post-template-tsx","path":"/posts/patches_firefox_relay/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"15cb4514-78bf-5d00-9a27-585e6bbc6902","html":"<p><img src=\"/media/firefoxrelay_cover.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"firefox-relay\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#firefox-relay\" aria-label=\"firefox relay permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Firefox Relay</h2>\n<p>Firefox 所推出的免費 Email 轉寄服務</p>\n<p>將寄到 Firefox 隨機生成 Email 地址的信件都轉寄到你的信箱，可免洗／一次性信箱，增加真實 Email 的匿名性並避免垃圾訊息。</p>\n<p>你是不是覺得很困惑，我為什麼需要這些隨機生成的匿名信箱？事實上，這樣可以大幅增加真實 Email 的匿名性，也可以藉由這個方法避免垃圾訊息喔～</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/firefoxrelay_website.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"優點\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%84%AA%E9%BB%9E\" aria-label=\"優點 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>優點</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>免費</li>\n<li>可信任：由 Firefox 推出</li>\n<li>方便使用：Firefox 瀏覽器有擴充套件</li>\n<li>方便管理：可隨時暫停轉寄／刪除</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"缺點\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BC%BA%E9%BB%9E\" aria-label=\"缺點 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>缺點</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>每個帳號只能生成五個 Email</li>\n<li>輸入／記憶上較不方便：Email 地址為隨機產生的</li>\n<li>目前不支援透過匿名信箱回信</li>\n<li>Email 復健不能大於 150KB</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"擴充套件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%93%B4%E5%85%85%E5%A5%97%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"擴充套件 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>擴充套件</h3>\n<p><img src=\"/media/firefoxrelay_extensionstore.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>Firefox 瀏覽器用戶可安裝 Firefox Relay 擴充套件，輸入 Email 時就能快速生成一個新的匿名信箱，使用上更快速方便</p>\n<p>目前不支援 Chrome 擴充套件</p>\n<p><img src=\"/media/firefoxrelay_extension.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2020-10-11-免費郵件轉寄服務//posts/patches_firefox_relay","tagSlugs":["/tag/firefox/","/tag/firefox-relay/","/tag/privacy/","/tag/anonymity/","/tag/browser-extension/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-10-11T23:16:23.986Z","description":"和大家介紹一個可以免費轉寄Email的服務。你是不是覺得很困惑，我為什麼需要這些隨機生成的匿名信箱？事實上，這樣可以大幅增加真實Email的匿名性，也可以藉由這個方法避免垃圾訊息喔～","tags":["Firefox","Firefox Relay","privacy","anonymity","browser extension"],"title":"免費郵件轉寄服務 - Firefox Relay","socialImage":"/media/firefoxrelay_cover.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2020-10-11-免費郵件轉寄服務//posts/patches_firefox_relay"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2246977889","2727970573","911332639"],"slicesMap":{}}